metadata.name: Pepe And His Sons
metadata.description:
The first series of Pepe's meta legacy is "pepe and his sons" (2022-Metaverse).

The meta legacy of "Laokoon and His Sons(1506-Rome)", one of the world cultural heritages, was left to Pepe and his sons. While preparing this legacy of Pepe, all details have been taken as reference in accordance with the original. The purpose of this collection is to leave a legacy in the name of Pepe to the meta world.

Video size : 1080x1960
File size : 40MB
File type : .mp4
